    "For each bootstrap iteration, we randomly resampled the whole sample size from the testing set with replacement.",
    "Smoothing spline fit in Fig. 2a was performed using npreg package in R with generalized crossvalidation method and default parameters 36.",
    "Ethical concerns MIMIC-IV is a free EHR dataset that is deidentified according to the Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPAA) Safe Harbor provision 27 Since we primarily used open source models such as LLaMA and ClinicalBERT from Huggingface, an open source repository of machine learning models 30 as well as CAML from github, and trained it on MIMIC, privacy risks are quite low.",
